testdata — Bot API JSON fixtures
=================================

All files in this directory are hand-written test fixtures. They do not
contain real bot tokens, real user IDs, or real chat IDs. All numeric IDs
and usernames are synthetic values chosen for readability in tests.

Files
-----

getme_response.json
  A synthetic Telegram Bot API getMe success response.
  Bot ID 123456789, username "testbot".

sendmessage_request.json
  A synthetic sendMessage request body (JSON-encoded parameters).
  Targets chat_id 987654321 with a plain HTML message.

sendmessage_response.json
  A synthetic sendMessage success response, echoing message_id 42.

getupdates_response.json
  A synthetic getUpdates success response containing one Update from a
  private chat. update_id 100000001, user "alice" (ID 111111111).

Provenance
----------
All fixtures are hand-written by the b2bdbg project authors.
No real Telegram API traffic was captured or stored here.
No secrets, tokens, or personally-identifiable information is present.
